+[float]
+[[define-cluster__uuid]]
+==== Define `cluster_uuid`
+To bind the metrics of {ls} to a specific cluster, define the `monitoring.cluster_uuid` 
+in the configuration file (logstash.yml):
+
+
+[source,yaml]
+----------------------------------
+monitoring.cluster_uuid: PRODUCTION_ES_CLUSTER_UUID
+----------------------------------
+
+
 
